The '''Bezimenne gas field''' [[natural gas field]] located on the continental shelf of the [[Black Sea]]. It was discovered in 1997 and developed by [[Chornomornaftogaz]]. It started commercial production in 1997. The total [[proven reserves]] of the Bezimenne gas field are around {{convert|140|e9cuft}}, and production is slated to be around {{convert|20|e6cuft/d}} in 2015.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://journals.tubitak.gov.tr/earth/issues/yer-12-21-5/yer-21-5-4-1102-4.pdf|title=Black Sea oil and gas fields|date=2009|publisher=tubitak.gov.tr|accessdate=2014-04-03}}</ref>
