//www.jcrystal.com/ Nanotube Modeler]</ref> * Materials Design MedeA<ref>[http://www.materialsdesign.com/medea Materials Design MedeA]</ref> * [[Materials Studio]] * [[MBN Explorer]] and MBN Studio<ref>{{cite book |title= Multiscale Modeling of Complex Molecular Structure and Dynamics with MBN Explorer||author1=I.A. Solov'yov |author2=A.V. Korol |author3=A.V. Solov'yov |year= 2017 |publisher=Springer International Publishing |isbn= 978-3-319-56085-4 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=MBN Explorer and MBN Studio software|url=http://mbnresearch.com/software-0}}</ref> * MD-kMC<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20090624043750/http://www.kintechlab.com/products/md-kmc/ MD-kMC]</ref> *[https://gitlab.com/acclab/parcas PARCAS]<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Nordlund|first=K.|last2=Ghaly|first2=M.|last3=Averback|first3=R. S.|last4=Caturla|first4=M.|last5=Diaz de la Rubia|first5=T.|last6=Tarus|first6=J.|date=1998-04-01|title=Defect production in collision cascades in elemental semiconductors and fcc metals|url=https://link.aps.org/doi/10.1103/PhysRevB.57.7556|journal=Physical Review B|volume=57|issue=13|pages=7556–7570|doi=10.1103/PhysRevB.57.7556}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=Ghaly|first=Mai.|last2=Nordlund|first2=Kai.|last3=Averback|first3=R. S.|date=1999|title=Molecular dynamics investigations of surface damage produced by kiloelectronvolt self-bombardment of solids|url=https://doi.org/10.1080/01418619908210332|journal=Philosophical Magazine A|language=en|volume=79|issue=4|pages=795–820|doi=10.1080/01418619908210332|issn=0141-8610|via=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=Nordlund|first=K.|date=1995|title=Molecular dynamics simulation of ion ranges in the 1–100 keV energy range|url=https://doi.org/10.1016/0927-0256(94)00085-Q|journal=Computational Materials Science|volume=3|issue=4|pages=448–456|doi=10.1016/0927-0256(94)00085-q|issn=0927-0256|via=}}</ref> – Open source [[molecular dynamics]] code * [[SAMSON]]: interactive carbon nanotube modeling<ref>[https://samson-connect.net/app/main?